---
import AppLayout from "../layouts/AppLayout.astro";
---

<AppLayout title="Personnel File | Daniel Agbemava" description="Security Clearance Level 4 // Personnel Record: Daniel Agbemava">
  <section class="about-page">
    <article class="personnel-file anim-fade-in">
      <header class="file-header">
        <div class="file-title-group">
          <div class="file-meta">Record ID: 8829-X-DANIEL // AUTH: LEVEL_4_CLEARANCE</div>
          <h1>DANIEL AGBEMAVA</h1>
          <div class="file-meta" style="margin-top: 0.5rem; color: var(--accent-orange)">Role: Software Engineer // Mobile & Backend Systems</div>
        </div>
        <div class="file-avatar-container anim-pop">
          <div class="file-avatar-glitch">
            <span class="about-avatar-emoji">🤖</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="file-section anim-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
        <div class="file-section-label">Operational Biography</div>
        <div class="file-content">
          Software engineer with 6+ years building mobile applications and backend
          services across fintech, AgTech, EdTech, and logistics. Spent four years
          supporting the open-source Flutter ecosystem at Nevercode, triaging over
          10,000 issues and contributing fixes to the framework. As a freelance engineer,
          has architected and delivered full-stack solutions for clients across multiple
          industries &mdash; from mobile banking apps deployed in Ghana and Egypt, to
          event-driven microservices powering agricultural traceability systems.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-section anim-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.35s">
        <div class="file-section-label">Service Record</div>
        <div class="file-content">
          <div class="service-record">
            <div class="service-entry">
              <span class="service-role">Freelance Software Engineer</span>
              <span class="service-org">Independent</span>
              <span class="service-tenure">2019 &ndash; Present</span>
            </div>
            <div class="service-entry">
              <span class="service-role">Open Source Support Engineer</span>
              <span class="service-org">Nevercode (Flutter)</span>
              <span class="service-tenure">2021 &ndash; 2026</span>
            </div>
            <div class="service-entry">
              <span class="service-role">Software Engineer</span>
              <span class="service-org">FASYL</span>
              <span class="service-tenure">2019 &ndash; 2020</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-section anim-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s">
        <div class="file-section-label">Mission Objectives</div>
        <div class="file-content">
          This site documents technical decisions, production debugging stories, and
          project work. It serves as a declassified archive of engineering challenges
          and solutions encountered across mobile, backend, and open-source work.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-section anim-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.65s">
        <div class="file-section-label">Technical Loadout</div>
        <div class="file-content">
          <div class="tech-grid" style="padding: 1rem; background: rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.3); border-radius: 4px;">
            <div class="tech-category">
              <div class="tech-category-label">Mobile</div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>Flutter / Dart</span></div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>React Native / Expo</span></div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>Riverpod / BLoC</span></div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>Kotlin</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-category">
              <div class="tech-category-label">Backend</div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>Spring Boot / Java</span></div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>NestJS / TypeScript</span></div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>Kafka</span></div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>PostgreSQL / MongoDB</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-category">
              <div class="tech-category-label">Infrastructure</div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>Docker</span></div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>Turborepo</span></div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>Firebase</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-category">
              <div class="tech-category-label">Integrations</div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>NFC / RFID / BLE</span></div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>Maps SDK</span></div>
              <div class="tech-badge"><span>Three.js / WebGL</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-section anim-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.8s">
        <div class="file-section-label">Field Notes</div>
        <div class="file-content">
          <ul class="field-notes">
            <li>Delivered mobile and backend solutions for 7+ clients across 4 industries</li>
            <li>Triaged and investigated 10,000+ issues in the Flutter open-source repository</li>
            <li>Built mobile banking apps deployed across international markets (Ghana, Egypt)</li>
            <li>Integrated hardware protocols (NFC, RFID, BLE) into logistics traceability systems</li>
            <li>Designed event-driven microservice architectures with Kafka and Spring Boot</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</AppLayout>
